{"tid":1316162,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟一個人攪緊隻INDIE H-GAME","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T05:47:40.000Z","uid":247878,"like":60,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"6f86743bcfc6d0a752829ccdfb66183aad0bd96f","tid":1316162,"uid":247878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"小弟人到中年，由做動畫，慢慢轉到去做game，兜兜轉轉事業無乜突破。<br />\n做得動畫嘅人，都係有啲個人主義，想做一啲自己嘅，於是毅然決定辭職，攪自己嘢，怕老左時更加無動力。<br />\n本身有幾個想法，但最後決定都係做一隻土炮Visual Novel HGAME。<br />\n隻GAME嘅第一章都攪得七七八八，本來想６月開始做多啲宣傳，但估唔到香港發生咁多事，亦都參加人生第一次嘅遊行。<br />\n唔講咁多喇，比啲圖大家睇下最實際。<br />\n大家有空入去比個LIKE，多啲人玩先比到動力去做下一章故事 。<br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/forbiddenfantasy2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fforbiddenfantasy2019&d=LzMeHrLekQtOmJ7gjClTQBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=c2643709\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/forbiddenfantasy2019</a><br />\nIG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/forbiddenfantasy2019/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fforbiddenfantasy2019%2F&d=LzMeHrLekQtOmJ7gjClTQBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=696db3eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/forbiddenfantasy2019/</a><br />\nPatreon : <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/forbiddenfantasy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fforbiddenfantasy&d=LzMeHrLekQtOmJ7gjClTQBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=c72b849c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/forbiddenfantasy</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqYVz0j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqYVz0j.jpg&h=18050fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXawSMX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXawSMX.jpg&h=6958ac49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d79Nq6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd79Nq6X.j